    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱丽丝误入了一个从未见过的植物之国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整个世界由像素描绘，宛如童话一般。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱丽丝的旅行以画风可爱的动画形式讲述。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/077b02b67fa0b3b25d05b947f06f7b3d.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/077b02b67fa0b3b25d05b947f06f7b3d.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/077b02b67fa0b3b25d05b947f06f7b3d.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与爱丽丝一起在地图中前进，完成结局吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/141d291c76287d085d8cc71147bcd896.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/141d291c76287d085d8cc71147bcd896.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/141d291c76287d085d8cc71147bcd896.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■《Slay the Alice》是一部短篇文字冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作只需要鼠标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家只需在地图中选择前进的道路，阅读随机触发的剧情，并决定爱丽丝的行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏没有动作、战斗、推理等任何复杂的要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请通过选项收集花，并到达地图终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/e5542b0367c19930d3381db05dd45c36.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/e5542b0367c19930d3381db05dd45c36.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/e5542b0367c19930d3381db05dd45c36.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■游戏概要</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・短篇游戏，游戏时间约30分钟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・操作简单，只需鼠标</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・没有动作、战斗和推理要素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・包含少许恐怖和残酷的内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・结局共4个 (＋1个附赠结局)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>■4个结局可供选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱丽丝的行动会导致结局发生少许变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成全部结局后，可解锁附赠结局。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/df2e3e5623b6c6dd43aa31567f19f538.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/df2e3e5623b6c6dd43aa31567f19f538.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/df2e3e5623b6c6dd43aa31567f19f538.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■游戏直播，创意指南</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 欢迎直播、发行、衍生作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 对于直播，请务必将 Steam 的“Slay the Alice”的 URL 粘贴到摘要字段中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 即使是盈利内容，也没有问题。</p>",
